  "keyFeatures": [
    "Ephemeral messaging with zero database persistence",
    "Public and private rooms with optional E2E encryption",
    "Real-time presence tracking and typing indicators",
    "Message reactions, replies, and read receipts",
    "Room moderation (kick, mute, vote kick, nuke)",
    "AFK detection and auto-kick",
    "Creator succession when creator leaves",
    "Room themes, tags, capacity limits, and TTL",
    "Content filtering and abuse reporting",
    "PWA support with mobile-optimized UI",
    "QR code and social sharing",
    "Swipe-to-reply gestures on mobile"
